metadata.name: No Face #1 "You at Apefest with one of  five women not paid to be there"
metadata.description:
No Face is a collection of 1/1 photos taken with top NFT creators, traders, and degens.  
Normally if you wanted people to believe you are an big time NFT player,  you would have to invest hundreds of hours of research and tens of thousands of dollars. But now anyone can claim to be an NFT power player and have the pics to prove it. Buying a No Face gives you complete rights to the photo.  Feel free to edit your face in or just claim that it is you in the NFT. Trevorwhatever.eth will even confirm that you are in the picture if you need him
